description:
Population Raster Federated States of Micronesia 2020
Data Input: HH locations from 2010 Housing listing conducted using GPS and Paper Assisted Personal Interview. Year Population Growth Rate of 0.22% has been applied to update population up to 2020
Household locations vector layer has been aggregated and transformed into a 100 m resolution raster.
name: Federated_States_Micronesia_Population_Grid_2020
